"title": "1429: prophecy, fulfilment of OT",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1429",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>All divinely inspired prophecy achieves its purpose. Scripture records the fulfilment of many prophecies.</p>\n<h2>The principle that all prophecy achieves its purpose</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:10-Isa55:11\">ISA 55:10–55:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:22\">DEU 18:22</a></p>\n<h2>Fulfilment of prophecy concerning individuals in the OT</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:35-1Kgs20:36\">1KI 20:35–20:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:15-1Kgs8:21\">1KI 8:15–8:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:4-2Chr6:11\">2CH 6:4–6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:23-1Kgs8:24\">1KI 8:23–8:24</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:14-2Chr6:15\">2CH 6:14–6:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:21-1Kgs13:22\">1KI 13:21–13:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:24-1Kgs13:26\">1KI 13:24–13:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:12-1Kgs14:13\">1KI 14:12–14:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:17-1Kgs14:18\">1KI 14:17–14:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:6\">2KI 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:17\">2KI 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:1-2Kgs7:2\">2KI 7:1–7:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:16-2Kgs7:18\">2KI 7:16–7:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:15-2Kgs22:20\">2KI 22:15–22:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:30\">2KI 23:30</a></p>\n<h2>Fulfilment of prophecy concerning the nation of Israel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:15\">1KI 12:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:29-1Kgs11:39\">1KI 11:29–11:39</a></p>\n<h2>Fulfilment of prophecy concerning the royal house</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:29\">1KI 15:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:7-1Kgs14:11\">1KI 14:7–14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:1-1Kgs16:7\">1KI 16:1–16:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:12\">1KI 16:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:20-1Kgs21:29\">1KI 21:20–21:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:30-2Kgs10:11\">2KI 9:30–10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:30\">2KI 10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:12\">2KI 15:12</a></p>\n<h2>Fulfilment of prophecy concerning battles</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:13-1Kgs20:21\">1KI 20:13–20:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:17\">1KI 22:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:35-1Kgs22:38\">1KI 22:35–22:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:20-2Kgs19:37\">2KI 19:20–19:37</a></p>\n<h2>Fulfilment of prophecy concerning the Babylonian exile</h2>\n<h3>The rise of the Babylonians</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:6-Hab1:11\">HAB 1:6–1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:17\">2CH 36:17</a></p>\n<h3>The fall of Jerusalem and exile of the population</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:17-2Kgs20:18\">2KI 20:17–20:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:10-2Kgs21:15\">2KI 21:10–21:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:2\">2KI 24:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:10-2Kgs24:16\">2KI 24:10–24:16</a></p>\n<h3>The fate of King Zedekiah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer21:3-Jer21:7\">JER 21:3–21:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:3-Jer32:5\">JER 32:3–32:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:12-Ezek12:14\">EZK 12:12–12:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:1-2Kgs25:7\">2KI 25:1–25:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer39:1-Jer39:7\">JER 39:1–39:7</a></p>\n<h3>The length of captivity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:10\">JER 29:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:21\">2CH 36:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:2\">DAN 9:2</a></p>\n<h2>Fulfilment of prophecy concerning Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:44\">LUK 24:44</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:31\">LUK 18:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:18\">ACT 3:18</a></p>\n<h2>Fulfilment of other prophecy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:14-Acts2:21\">ACT 2:14–2:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28-Joel2:32\">JOL 2:28–2:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:26\">JOS 6:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:34\">1KI 16:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:1-1Kgs13:3\">1KI 13:1–13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:16-2Kgs23:18\">2KI 23:16–23:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:14\">1KI 17:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:16\">1KI 17:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:17-Matt2:18\">MAT 2:17–2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:15\">JER 31:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:1-Matt3:3\">MAT 3:1–3:3</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:2-Mark1:4\">MRK 1:2–1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:1-Luke3:6\">LUK 3:1–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:3\">ISA 40:3</a></p>\n<h2>Prophecies modified before fulfilment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:20-1Kgs21:26\">1KI 21:20–21:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:27-1Kgs21:29\">1KI 21:27–21:29</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:1\">ISA 38:1</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:1\">2KI 20:1</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:4-Isa38:5\">ISA 38:4–38:5</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:4-2Kgs20:6\">2KI 20:4–20:6</a></p>",
